    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically, this chassis is superlative: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Beisan components. Preventative rod bearing replacement has been performed to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains reliable for years to come. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with fresh bushings throughout, preserving the communicative steering rack and the mechanical grip provided by the Variable M Differential Lock. With zero deferred maintenance and a completely stock configuration, this is a rare opportunity to own a pinnacle of Bavarian engineering.",
