      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like luster with professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and fragrant, free from any bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documenting preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. From the pristine engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, this car represents the pinnacle of its class for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
